title: td-route-trees
message: >-
  If you use td-route-trees, please cite it using the metadata
  from this file.
type: software
authors:
  - given-names: Florian
    family-names: Rascoussier
    alias: Onyr
    affiliation: IMT Atlantique; INSA Lyon
