url: "https://github.com/0nyr/td-route-trees"
repository-code: "https://github.com/0nyr/td-route-trees"
abstract: >-
  td-route-trees is a study repository for fast move evaluation in
  duration-minimization time-dependent vehicle routing. It compares
  route ready-time function trees, LCA-BST style structures, and
  prefix/suffix composition-reuse techniques on a shared exact
  non-decreasing continuous piecewise-linear engine, with validation
  against the MAMUT routing checker.
keywords:
  - time-dependent vehicle routing problem
  - TDVRPTW
  - TDVRP
  - vehicle routing problem
  - local search
  - move evaluation
  - route duration
  - piecewise-linear functions
  - NDCPWLF
  - route trees
  - benchmarking
  - operations research
  - combinatorial optimization
  - research software
